The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, august
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | colombian    |
| Birthday           | september       | august   |
| Flower         | tulip   | dahlia     |

